Sounds like 180 off then.

Remember:

Intake open, piston is pulled down.Fuel/air comes in.
Intake closes, piston comes up(Compressed fuel Mixture, TDC, fire).
Piston is pushed down.
Exhaust Valve opens, piston is pushed up. Exhaust releases.

http://www.benplace.com/4cycles.htm

